If it?s dangerous, they want to find it, hold it, study it, and even ride it! Developing their own interaction techniques, Manny and Mark are world-renowned for their ability to get closer than anyone to the largest predators in the wild?and this footage proves it. This is your chance to ride shotgun with Manny and the Jackass crew!
